{"tid":1652003,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇B說球會使用「高科技買人」","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T04:43:45.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"07d4314d847cbb33db1272053bbead7c61b816b1","tid":1652003,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】英超豪門曼聯今季頹勢依舊，有傳主帥蘇斯克查希望高層首肯，引入科學方式追蹤潛力球星。<br />\n<br />\n不少球會都有自己的一套球探系統，但曼聯主帥蘇斯克查（Ole Gunnar Solskjaer）似乎認為己隊的球探仍未足夠，有傳他正遊說球會高層與一所西班牙的足球顧問公司合作。該公司有著一套高科技系統，分析、追蹤世界各地的球員，手上掌握多達10萬名足球員的資料，非常適合尋找新將。<br />\n<br />\n這種「高科技買人」方式並非新事物，近年表現如日方中的利物浦其實早早就已經求助類似的顧問公司，如13年加盟的古天奴（Philippe Coutinho）就是以同樣方法發掘出來的球星。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，有傳蘇B連購買球員的手法都希望有所改變，有機會效法利物浦未雨綢繆的方式。當年紅軍早在轉會窗開啟前半年已經與雲迪克達成轉會協議，蘇斯克查深信這種提早斟介的方式有利球會發展，比起轉會窗內尋找「開綠燈」求售的球員更為有效。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"6b9139d8167ec3c3d28a7399ab5652ba79f3710d","tid":1652003,"uid":15626,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"係咪用fm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcded98d02433e509c562a46586939b96e8d248","tid":1652003,"uid":114328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6b9139d8167ec3c3d28a7399ab5652ba79f3710d","tid":1652003,"uid":15626,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:58:39.000Z","msg":"係咪用fm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:32:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/football-manager-solskjaer-manchester-united-15782979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.manchestereveningnews.co.uk%2Fsport%2Ffootball%2Ffootball-news%2Ffootball-manager-solskjaer-manchester-united-15782979&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=1f7c67df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/football-manager-solskjaer-manchester-united-15782979</a><br />\n你冇講錯 sob玩fm"},{"pid":"1719ff5b5b334ccca88ca4bd7287e26aeea5638a","tid":1652003,"uid":198329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"仲以為Youtube"},{"pid":"5d2f0c7e6db1f64dd7f623afd3c6b6a2fa25adb4","tid":1652003,"uid":97997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1719ff5b5b334ccca88ca4bd7287e26aeea5638a","tid":1652003,"uid":198329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:42:16.000Z","msg":"仲以為Youtube"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"篇文講個system應該就係個球員片database，好多球會用咗好耐<br />\n咁樣唔怕俾經理人啲球王片呃，甚至可以低價買到啱用嘅人"},{"pid":"2ba7183dd9f984081a259ab97511e2ebfa93161b","tid":1652003,"uid":103230,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:48:07.000Z","msg":"其實冇意思<br />\n你買左唔識教<br />\n一樣成長唔到"},{"pid":"2adcf4fda33d488de3eabff218c714d8c84cfee1","tid":1652003,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"用fifa數據買人？"},{"pid":"5fba560f753726c58ab4f3a1d9e12c4b8af90d8e","tid":1652003,"uid":6070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"唔用fax機？"},{"pid":"ef448c73b4616056f62d4e48d860b72e876acbfa","tid":1652003,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"fifa"},{"pid":"f6bf45354dada369aacc5d4d5b9a8a117bf615a1","tid":1652003,"uid":47268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2adcf4fda33d488de3eabff218c714d8c84cfee1","tid":1652003,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:50:17.000Z","msg":"用fifa數據買人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"Fm好似準啲"},{"pid":"a959f26c232f3cb85b049e715f4e5fbfb72d1e5c","tid":1652003,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"fm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e698bb8f2a02ad705a4ee232